        <h2 id="what-is">What is Outranking?</h2>
        <p>Outranking is an AI-assisted SEO writing platform. The product idea: a single workflow that takes you from keyword to optimized draft without juggling Surfer + Frase + ChatGPT + Docs. The bet is that bundling saves both money and switching cost.</p>

